{
    "name": "Überweisung Automation - Physio",
    "nodes": [
        {
            "parameters": {
                "httpMethod": "POST",
                "path": "referral-upload",
                "responseMode": "lastNode",
                "options": {}
            },
            "id": "webhook-trigger",
            "name": "Webhook - Fotoğraf Al",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
            "position": [
                250,
                300
            ],
            "typeVersion": 1
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "fileName": "={{ $json.body.business_id }}/{{ $json.fileName }}"
            },
            "id": "storage-upload",
            "name": "Supabase Storage - Fotoğraf Yükle",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
            "position": [
                500,
                300
            ]
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "url": "https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions",
                "method": "POST",
                "sendHeaders": true,
                "headerParameters": {
                    "parameters": [
                        {
                            "name": "Authorization",
                            "value": "Bearer {{ $env.OPENROUTER_API_KEY }}"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "Content-Type",
                            "value": "application/json"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                "sendBody": true,
                "bodyParameters": {
                    "parameters": [
                        {
                            "name": "model",
                            "value": "google/gemini-2.0-flash-thinking:free"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "messages",
                            "value": [
                                {
                                    "role": "user",
                                    "content": {
                                        "type": "text",
                                        "text": "Du bist ein medizinischer Assistent. Analysiere das hochgeladene Überweisungsdokument und extrahiere die folgenden Informationen:\n\n1. Patientenvorname (Vorname)\n2. Patientennachname (Nachname)  \n3. Geburtsdatum (Format: YYYY-MM-DD)\n4. Anzahl der Sitzungen (seans_sayisi)\n5. Behandlungsart (tedavi_turu)\n6. Hausbesuch (ja/nein)\n7. Diagnose\n8. Arztname (falls vorhanden)\n\nAntworte NUR im JSON-Format:\n```json\n{\n  \"ad\": \"Vorname\",\n  \"soyad\": \"Nachname\",\n  \"dogum_tarihi\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n  \"seans_sayisi\": 6,\n  \"tedavi_turu\": \"Physiotherapie\",\n  \"hausbesuch\": false,\n  \"diagnose\": \"Rückenschmerzen\",\n  \"arzt_name\": \"Dr. Müller\"\n}\n```\n\nWICHTIG: \n- Antworte NUR mit gültigem JSON, keine Erklärungen\n- Wenn du dir bei einem Feld nicht sicher bist, setze es auf null\n- Das Geburtsdatum muss im Format YYYY-MM-DD sein\n- Zero Retention: Diese Daten werden NICHT für Training verwendet"
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "role": "user",
                                    "content": {
                                        "type": "image_url",
                                        "image_url": {
                                            "url": "={{ $json.imageUrl }}"
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                "options": {}
            },
            "id": "ai-vision",
            "name": "OpenRouter - Gemini Vision",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
            "position": [
                750,
                300
            ]
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "url": "https://njvuclullotbksskpwgk.supabase.co/rest/v1/referral_drafts",
                "method": "POST",
                "sendHeaders": true,
                "headerParameters": {
                    "parameters": [
                        {
                            "name": "apikey",
                            "value": "{{ $env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY }}"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "Authorization",
                            "value": "Bearer {{ $env.SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY }}"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "Content-Type",
                            "value": "application/json"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "Prefer",
                            "value": "return=representation"
                        }
                    ]
                },
                "sendBody": true,
                "bodyParameters": {
                    "parameters": [
                        {
                            "name": "owner_id",
                            "value": "={{ $json.body.business_id }}"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "raw_ai_data",
                            "value": "={{ $json.aiResponse }}"
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "patient_vorname",
